      <title>巴西石油公司股价因董事长将离职的报道而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/petrobras-shares-fall-on-report-that-chairman-will-leave-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三位知情人士称，巴西石油公司董事长皮埃特罗·门德斯将离开这家石油生产商，担任巴西石油监管机构的董事，这让投资者对该公司的股息政策感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/petrobras-shares-fall-on-report-that-chairman-will-leave-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 20:59:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的博伊文表示，全球债券比美国国债更受青睐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/blackrock-s-boivin-says-global-bonds-favored-over-us-treasuries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德投资研究所所长让·博文 (Jean Boivin) 表示，由于通胀压力加大，美联储明年将不得不保持观望态度，投资者应该青睐全球债券，而非期限较长的美国国债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/blackrock-s-boivin-says-global-bonds-favored-over-us-treasuries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 20:50:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
