    <item>
      <title>巴尼耶政府倒台后，法国债券期货保持上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/french-bond-futures-hold-gains-after-barnier-s-government-falls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞加入左翼联盟推翻政府之后，法国债券期货守住了早前的涨幅，这为进一步的政治争论奠定了基础，数月来，这场争论一直对法国资产造成压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/french-bond-futures-hold-gains-after-barnier-s-government-falls</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 19:41:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织内部监管机构批评其对巨额贷款的处理方式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/imf-s-internal-watchdog-critiques-its-handling-of-largest-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，国际货币基金组织的内部监管机构批评了该银行向阿根廷和埃及等陷入困境的借款人发放异常巨额贷款的程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/imf-s-internal-watchdog-critiques-its-handling-of-largest-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 18:54:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币在数字货币支持者入选美国证券交易委员会后恢复上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bitcoin-btc-churns-near-96-000-as-crypto-awaits-trump-s-next-step</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在数字资产倡导者保罗·阿特金斯被美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普选中担任美国证券交易委员会主席后，加密货币投机者将比特币价格瞄准了具有里程碑意义的 10 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bitcoin-btc-churns-near-96-000-as-crypto-awaits-trump-s-next-step</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 00:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
